Known organism to media mapping

A central resource within KOMODO is a listing of organism-media pairs that are known to enable growth, as provided by the DSMZ and developed over many years of attempting to culture organisms. There are ~18,000 such pairings that are known. Here, we list all of the strains in KOMODO, along with media they are known to grow on. Click on any medium name for more details.
